sequenceDiagram
  participant P as PC
  participant R as Raspberry Pi
  participant I as iPhone
  P->>I: Tailscale ON + RTSP Server Start
  P->>R: SSH / tailscale status
  P->>R: ffprobe rtsp://<iphone_ip>:8554/stream
  P->>R: go2rtc.yaml update + docker restart go2rtc
  P->>R: ffprobe rtsp://127.0.0.1:8554/cam
  P->>R: systemctl restart rover-backend/front
  P->>R: curl /api/health, /api/network/status
  P->>R: Web GCS check
